node.name: WRFV4.-Manunal
node.description: This page is meant to guide you through the steps of compiling WRF. It will take a beginning user through the processes of ensuring the computer environment is set up correctly, to testing the components and their compatibility with each other, then to installing WRF and WPS, and finally to some guidance for preparing to run WPS and then WRF.
